extendedInfo.description: Justin Bieber Fan App Call Justin with one touch on the screen ! Are You A True Justin Bieber Fan? Do you want to hear his voice on the phone ? This app gives you a chance to call him and talk with Bieber. Could You Date Justin Bieber ? The answer is YES, this application will help you to do that. This app looks like it is able to: -Get Justin Bieber phone number -Call Justin -Manage to arrange a date with him But it is just a fun app, you won't get the real Bieber on the phone, it is just recorded voice He is very popular pop musician, actor, and singer-songwriter.  Do you want to call  him ? Install this app and do that any time you want , but of course a face call :) Bieber has received numerous awards, including both Artist of the Year Awards at the 2010 American Music Awards and the 2012 American Music Awards, and was nominated for Best New Artist and Best Pop Vocal Album at the 53rd Grammy Awards With a global fan base, termed as "Beliebers", and over 33 million followers on Twitter, he was named by Forbes magazine in 2012 as the third-most powerful celebrity in the world Do you think that is impossible to find Justin phone number ? no it is not, with this app you can call with just a few touches on the screen. disclaimer: This is an fun app made by Justin fans , it only a joke app.
